title: Nu Shooz - Poolside + bonus remixes (1986)
description:
Excellent pop breakthrough of 1986!!  Now if this sound doesn&#039;t cause a change in future pop music - nothing will!  

Who knew that the word "trance" would ever become a dance music term??  Referring to the track - "You Put Me In a Trance"

Nu Shooz also recorded another album called "Told U So" which was released in 1988.
If anyone has this album - please PLEASE share and upload so I can get this...

Enjoy and bob your head - "ba-ba, I CAN&#039;T WAIT"
